Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.10,0:22:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}將銀色的月與光影交織 Spiral sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.30,0:22:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}互相糾纏不確定的 Relation 時而將羈絆的心靈束縛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.60,0:22:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}動不了？ 還是不想動？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.10,0:22:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}將孤獨轉化為強悍！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.82,0:22:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Drastic my soul 本能地引導著我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.58,0:22:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Drastic myself 超越夢想向著新的自我...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.12,0:22:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Drastic my soul 想去確認在此處生存的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.22,0:22:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Drastic myself 衝破更深邃的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.22,0:23:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1000)}I believe in Drastic my soul
